#: resources/xnec2c.glade:10972
msgid ""
"Power transfer n^γ relative to this frequency step's peak.\n"
"γ = 0.5 expands weak regions, γ = 1 is linear amplitude, γ = 2 shows the "
"squared magnitude: |I|² is proportional to per-segment dissipated power (and "
"its radiated-power contribution via radiation resistance), |q|² to stored "
"electrostatic energy.\n"
"Adjust γ in the animate dialog."
msgstr ""
"Pemindahan kuasa n^γ relatif kepada puncak langkah frekuensi ini.\n"
"γ = 0.5 mengembangkan kawasan lemah, γ = 1 adalah amplitud linear, γ = 2 "
"menunjukkan magnitud kuasa dua: |I|² berkadar dengan kuasa terlesap bagi "
"setiap segmen (dan sumbangan kuasa sinarannya melalui rintangan sinaran), |q|"
"² dengan tenaga elektrostatik tersimpan.\n"
"Laraskan γ dalam dialog animasi."

